@startuml user-journey-share
title undef-terminal — Terminal Sharing Journey

skinparam backgroundColor #ffffff
skinparam defaultFontColor #333333
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #2563eb
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #d1d5db
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #d1d5db
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #f3f4f6
skinparam actorBorderColor #6b7280
skinparam noteBorderColor #d1d5db
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #f9fafb

actor "Tim\n(admin)" as Tim
participant "uterm share\n(CLI)" as CLI
participant "Server\n(TermHub)" as S
participant "Jane's Browser\n(operator)" as Jane
participant "Red Hawk's Browser\n(viewer)" as RH

== Tim starts sharing ==

Tim -> CLI : uterm share
CLI -> S : WebSocket connect\n(worker role + bearer token)
S -> CLI : hello {input_mode: "hijack",\n  presence_enabled: true}
note over CLI : PTY process spawns\nTerminal is live

== Jane joins via link ==

Jane -> S : WebSocket connect\n(operator role + JWT)
S -> Jane : hello {worker_online: true,\n  presence_enabled: true}
S -> Jane : presence_sync {users: [Tim]}
Jane -> S : presence_update {scroll_line: 0,\n  name: "Jane"}
S -> CLI : presence_update — Jane joined
note over Jane : Sees Tim's terminal\nTim's avatar glows\n(pulsing border = controller)

== Red Hawk joins ==

RH -> S : WebSocket connect\n(viewer role + JWT)
S -> RH : hello {worker_online: true}
S -> RH : presence_sync {users: [Tim, Jane]}
RH -> S : presence_update {name: "Red Hawk"}
S -> Jane : presence_update — Red Hawk joined
S -> CLI : presence_update — Red Hawk joined
note over Jane : Red Hawk's avatar appears\nEdge bar shows their viewport

== Live collaboration ==

CLI -> S : PTY bytes (terminal output)
S -> Jane : terminal data
S -> RH : terminal data

Jane -> S : scroll to line 42
S -> RH : presence_update {scroll_line: 42, user: Jane}
note over RH : Jane's edge bar moves to line 42

note over Jane,RH : DeckMux overlay shows:\n• Tim's avatar — pulsing border (controller)\n• Jane's avatar — at line 42\n• Red Hawk's avatar — position shown in edge bar

== Jane requests control ==

Jane -> S : control_request {target: tim}
S -> CLI : control_request_notification {from: "Jane"}
note over Tim : Toast in terminal:\n"Jane requesting control"\n[Hand over] [Deny]
Tim -> CLI : accepts handover
CLI -> S : control_handover {to: jane}
S -> Jane : control_transfer {reason: "handover"}
S -> RH : control_transfer {to: jane}
note over Jane : Jane's border now pulses\nJane can type

@enduml
